WEBVTT

00:00:25.687 --> 00:00:30.303
This was an apt answer, I thought,

00:00:30.327 --> 00:00:32.732
because while it is easy
to get into a relationship

00:00:32.756 --> 00:00:34.466
it’s not so easy to honor
the relationship,

00:00:34.496 --> 00:00:36.109
and to do it lovingly is a tall order.

00:00:36.109 --> 00:00:38.543
Our speaker Manju Kapur believes that

00:00:38.567 --> 00:00:42.303
it is even tougher for Indian men.

00:00:42.327 --> 00:00:44.863
Why is it like that?

00:00:44.887 --> 00:00:45.887
Well I would like to know
the answer for sure.

00:00:45.887 --> 00:00:48.527
After all, I am an Indian man, too.

00:00:48.527 --> 00:00:49.967
On TED Talks India Nayi Soch

00:00:49.967 --> 00:00:52.044
to answer this question
we have with us today

00:00:52.044 --> 00:00:55.143
Delhi based award winning novelist,
Manju Kapur.

00:00:55.167 --> 00:00:57.937
Star Plus’s popular show
is based on her novel “Custody.”

00:00:57.977 --> 00:01:00.047
“Yeh Hai Mohabbatien"